    "Two illustrative examples of injection-recovery mismatch are shown in Fig. 14.",
    "The top panel shows one of the GWB recoveries.",
    "Although the injection did not present particular features (e.g.",
    "loud CGWs), for this specific noise realization, the recovered signal has a shallow slope with a median value of γ = 3.10.",
    "Similar cases have been observed when injecting a pure γ = 13/3 power law with the createGWB function of libstempo (Vallisneri 2020)."
